# Commits

When preparing commits, prefer the **user’s Cursor git safety + conventional-commit rules** (`feat:` / `fix:` / `refactor:` imperatives, body as needed).

Do **not** enable `alwaysApply` duplicate commit policies that conflict with those instructions.
